{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Under the hero, create a new section with id="shop-by-category" in the same visual style as the hero and tentree.com. Use a soft neutral background and a centered max-width container. Add an H2: “Shop Premium Wall Art by Category” and a short paragraph. Below, create 3 pill-style tabs: Paintings, Metal Posters, Acrylic Posters. Each tab should show a horizontally scrollable row of product cards from a collection picker. Each card: rounded white card, soft shadow, product image on top, product title as H3, small meta line, and a full-width pill “Buy Now” button linking to the product URL. Only one tab’s cards are visible at a time. Match spacing, rounded corners and hover feel to tentree-style product rows.
{% enddoc %}
